<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe5d74f8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7625a"><num value="7625a">§ 7625a.</num><heading> Statutory construction</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The parenthetical cross references in any provision of this chapter to other provisions of the chapter, or other provisions of law, where the words “relating to” or “pertaining to” are used, are made only for convenience, and shall be given no legal effect.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe5d74f9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-07-14/ch360">July 14, 1955, ch. 360</ref>, title III, § 326, as added <ref href="/us/pl/95/190/s14/a/84">Pub. L. 95–190, § 14(a)(84)</ref>, <date date="1977-11-16">Nov. 16, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/1404">91 Stat. 1404</ref>; renumbered § 325, <ref href="/us/pl/96/300/s1/c">Pub. L. 96–300, § 1(c)</ref>, <date date="1980-07-02">July 2, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/831">94 Stat. 831</ref>; renumbered § 326, <ref href="/us/pl/98/213/s11">Pub. L. 98–213, § 11</ref>, <date date="1983-12-08">Dec. 8, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/1461">97 Stat. 1461</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbe5d74fa-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbe5d74fb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idbe5d74fc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 326 of act <date date="1955-07-14">July 14, 1955</date>, was renumbered section 327 by <ref href="/us/pl/98/213">Pub. L. 98–213</ref> and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s7626">section 7626 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
